				<td colspan="2" height="100%" valign="top"><span class="postbody">Guild members are eligible for a number of benefits:
<br />

<br />
<b>Item Drops</b> - When mobs die, they leave things on their corpses which we must put away in a safe place so that old ladies don't trip on them and children don't maim themselves. We handle item drops through an auction system in which guild members bid on the items they want with points that they earn. As Sun Tzu says in the Art of War: "Rewards are necessary in order to make the soldiers see the advantage of beating the enemy; thus, when you capture spoils from the enemy they must be used as rewards so that all your men may have a keen desire to fight, each on his own account."
<br />

<br />
<b>Steamy Guild Chat!</b> - No explanation needed. 
<br />

<br />
<b>Quest Help</b> - Some quests require more two or more groups. Guild members may purchase a raid for these quests.
<br />

<br />
<b>Steamy Guild Chat</b>! - I said no explanation, so stop asking, perv.
<br />

<br />
<b>Camaraderie</b>! - The greatest benefit of all, of course, is the friends you'll make while part of this guild. We take great care to select mature, intelligent adults and the result is (trite as it may sound) fun.
<br />

<br />

<br />
Some of this help is reserved for members who have shown that they're in it for the long term. Here are the member tiers and the benefits that are reserved for each tier: 
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Recruit:</span> Earn points for raids, but may not spend them.
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Member1:</span> As you move from the test of patience as an applicant into full membership you obtain member level 1. This distinguishes you as a member of this guild and your first star. 
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Member2:</span> As you obtain 3 months of senority in this guild you are able to obtain the ranking of 2 stars and member level 2. 
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Member3:</span> As you obtain 6 months of senority in this guild you are able to obtain the ranking of 3 stars and member level 3. There is a 100 dkp bonus or the average % of the 5 most current raid values whichever is greater at that point.
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Member4:</span> As you obtain 12 months of senority in this guild you are able to obtain the ranking of 4 stars and member level 4. There is a 200 dkp bonus or 2x the average % of the 5 most current raid values whichever is greater at that point. This is the highest ranking you as a guildmember are able to obtain thru tenure alone.
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Member5:</span> As you obtain 18 months of senority as well as MVP or officer status at some point during your tenure in this guild you are able to obtain the ranking of 5 stars and member level 5. MVP is awarded once every month for outstanding service to the guild. MVP is determined thru nominations and evaluated and determined by Vova. There is a 200 dkp bonus or 2x the average % of the 5 most current raid values whichever is greater at that point. 
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Member6:</span> As you obtain 24 months of senority you are available to be voted into member level 6 and recieve your final 6th star. You must be nominated for member level 6 and an anonymous vote must be conducted on your behalf. Nominations must be sent via PM to Vova and Vova will conduct the vote. Honorable and loyal service to the guild is the consideration to be made. There is a 300 dkp bonus or 3x the average % of the 5 most current raid values whichever is greater at that point.</span><br /><span class="gensmall"><br /><br />Last edited by vova on 10.29 05.44pm; edited 7 times in total</span></td>
			</tr>
